reviews.review_text:
s1 vg, skip s2 Vg recording sonically, but as the info file states, there's overpowering crowd babbling (the risk w/FOBs).

Playing-wise, Set 1 is very good, but set 2 starts to fall apart a few songs in and is really a careless mess.
